{"tid":1222717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重溫】如何為美軍帶路","createTime":"2019-06-14T13:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T17:35:23.000Z","uid":98826,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"03c437594fe827f7b642c476c2a4fed4308b1ca8","tid":1222717,"uid":98826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"給美軍帶路的步驟：<br />\n<br />\n一、準備工作：<br />\n<br />\n1、見到美軍來了，要趕快圍上去表示善意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6r9elCjWa2U/V4OgM8rf_4I/AAAAAAAABFw/WZYjCWFBdgM2R3yy03cGkbt0NK101PvNACLcB/s1600/640.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-6r9elCjWa2U%2FV4OgM8rf_4I%2FAAAAAAAABFw%2FWZYjCWFBdgM2R3yy03cGkbt0NK101PvNACLcB%2Fs1600%2F640.jpeg&h=2f72c98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2、與美軍拉家常，比如問他你叫什麼名？ 家裡幾口人？ 養了幾條狗？ 結婚了嗎？ 軍隊收入怎麼樣?要讓大兵感受到生活的不公平和專政。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hhKbYF1hIIc/V4OgvkZCXtI/AAAAAAAABF0/mFFp4u_FM2wWB19CCtq800f0aMWEWDgJgCLcB/s1600/641.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-hhKbYF1hIIc%2FV4OgvkZCXtI%2FAAAAAAAABF0%2FmFFp4u_FM2wWB19CCtq800f0aMWEWDgJgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F641.jpeg&h=3132a268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3、等於大兵熟悉了環境，幫助破除埋伏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-dufloBncI3A/V4Og7-fcF6I/AAAAAAAABF8/7T5P19yq9TQl-PrDSiLs6kqgNL5HcnXFQCLcB/s1600/642.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-dufloBncI3A%2FV4Og7-fcF6I%2FAAAAAAAABF8%2F7T5P19yq9TQl-PrDSiLs6kqgNL5HcnXFQCLcB%2Fs1600%2F642.jpeg&h=12c5e4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二 、 指路：<br />\n <br />\n 1、 如果你不想帶路可以從地圖上指出重要目標地點之類的信息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-5W8NcZoxXZQ/V4OiDO9JjvI/AAAAAAAABGI/T8AYVJf9wo4ZZ76jl0JAy9FYzQHXKwXtACLcB/s1600/643.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-5W8NcZoxXZQ%2FV4OiDO9JjvI%2FAAAAAAAABGI%2FT8AYVJf9wo4ZZ76jl0JAy9FYzQHXKwXtACLcB%2Fs1600%2F643.jpeg&h=a1a804b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三、帶路：<br />\n<br />\n1、以上所有的行動都是為了這一刻的到來，平時苦練的follow me，this way為的就是這一刻。 帶他去暴政辦公地，武力鎮壓處，非正常關押處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-w24uTcJAFvw/V4OjFrdHNTI/AAAAAAAABGU/awGKtJqSaZ0bbWuWycrhvRmPqrV9lr4vgCLcB/s1600/644.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-w24uTcJAFvw%2FV4OjFrdHNTI%2FAAAAAAAABGU%2FawGKtJqSaZ0bbWuWycrhvRmPqrV9lr4vgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F644.jpeg&h=f1a02c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2、英語練的好，帶路帶到老。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-o03XzzNetfw/V4OjSJVv9jI/AAAAAAAABGY/HCnZHi7vxFQ9KkvSfzaMnu5EkD-ymaK1gCLcB/s1600/645.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-o03XzzNetfw%2FV4OjSJVv9jI%2FAAAAAAAABGY%2FHCnZHi7vxFQ9KkvSfzaMnu5EkD-ymaK1gCLcB%2Fs1600%2F645.jpeg&h=c7e640a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3、This Way.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4K2_bAD_NpQ/V4OjgheNLAI/AAAAAAAABGc/Ymmoz4HXdQ4yxA80z9uKRNwB_iVE9XyOQCLcB/s1600/646.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-4K2_bAD_NpQ%2FV4OjgheNLAI%2FAAAAAAAABGc%2FYmmoz4HXdQ4yxA80z9uKRNwB_iVE9XyOQCLcB%2Fs1600%2F646.jpeg&h=91656967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4、 Over There. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-neh7haio0ZA/V4Okf-cfm8I/AAAAAAAABGs/tgDJnGJP7kQObdMY8bHUiZTMv8i_1YRrgCLcB/s1600/647.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-neh7haio0ZA%2FV4Okf-cfm8I%2FAAAAAAAABGs%2FtgDJnGJP7kQObdMY8bHUiZTMv8i_1YRrgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F647.jpeg&h=9fd3ce32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5、You sure? Yes yes，is here.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-LopwoG-YIaA/V4Ok8WRT_WI/AAAAAAAABGw/GutGdasjoJE4CUdtC9TcCmfatSJ8ePlcgCLcB/s1600/648.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LopwoG-YIaA%2FV4Ok8WRT_WI%2FAAAAAAAABGw%2FGutGdasjoJE4CUdtC9TcCmfatSJ8ePlcgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F648.jpeg&h=03203d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 6、對於年齡尚小還不能懂事的，美軍也有賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-TLC-W8ED55U/V4Olewsw2YI/AAAAAAAABG8/GykVttcpJyIKIizd7PIqQ8l3If9BL_87QCLcB/s1600/649.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-TLC-W8ED55U%2FV4Olewsw2YI%2FAAAAAAAABG8%2FGykVttcpJyIKIizd7PIqQ8l3If9BL_87QCLcB%2Fs1600%2F649.jpeg&h=9b6c16a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.   少年報告美軍，前面有Ｘ匪殘餘埋伏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/HwcFiYalOj_2klBnxpuAIw==/5735615600433130736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2FHwcFiYalOj_2klBnxpuAIw%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130736.jpg&h=56d49488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.   帶完路，有賞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/-SjCgPYyVZltuda7UX16pQ==/5735615600433130738.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2F-SjCgPYyVZltuda7UX16pQ%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130738.jpg&h=95b7ce48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9.    一人帶路，全家有賞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/uO2rQSa1xAQtU651uydHxg==/5735615600433130740.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2FuO2rQSa1xAQtU651uydHxg%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130740.jpg&h=ba039f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10.   帶完路，你和美軍就是朋友了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/vY07eZEZH4hG90j_x-O0hA==/5735615600433130741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2FvY07eZEZH4hG90j_x-O0hA%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130741.jpg&h=0645591f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/7IbK3gSFvvlG6pgVVSA6fA==/5735615600433130745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2F7IbK3gSFvvlG6pgVVSA6fA%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130745.jpg&h=9a9804bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帶路不分年齡。一人帶路，全家光榮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s9.sinaimg.cn/middle/5a1c70bfg96972682caf8&amp;690\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs9.sinaimg.cn%2Fmiddle%2F5a1c70bfg96972682caf8%26690&h=a1b84301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉載：<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_5a1c70bf0100o4se.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2Fblog_5a1c70bf0100o4se.html&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjQFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=b6273cb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_5a1c70bf0100o4se.html</a>"},{"pid":"8a306b6d0487ad6773822237b2aede9631bbdb37","tid":1222717,"uid":249971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:49:50.000Z","msg":"新浪出呢d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a87b40213548625549db8972a26cb4d4254259c","tid":1222717,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">（希望大家廣傳民陣fb呼籲！）</span><br />\n<br />\n毋忘年輕人付出，誓撤回逃犯條例！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣反送中遊行</span><br />\n日期：6月16日（星期日）<br />\n遊行開始時間：2:30pm<br />\n遊行起點：維多利亞公園<span style=\"color: gold;\">（有可能再加入其他起點同時前進，請留意民陣fb最新消息）</span><br />\n遊行終點：政府總部<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核心目標：撤回逃犯條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣三罷反送中集會</span><br />\n日期：6月17日（星期一）<br />\n集會地點：立法會外<br />\n當日行動：三罷（罷工罷市罷課）<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（留意返星期一嘅三罷集會係未有時間，要等民陣fb睇下佢地點安排）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核心目標：撤回逃犯條例</span>"},{"pid":"0c6aa38278a413e0488b6aad10e6a5d33d5303f8","tid":1222717,"uid":79173,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"this way sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0142f7e19b7213174e7592b850480fcf56bac8","tid":1222717,"uid":120678,